  <title>How to Configure JDBC-ODBC Support</title>
  <!--Proofed-->
  <body>
    <p>To configure the support for a JDBC-ODBC database follow this procedure:<ol>
        <li><?oxy_comment_start author="steven_higgs" timestamp="20141224T113818+0200" comment="Topic missing for &quot;How to Configure a JDBC-ODBC Data Source&quot;?"?>Configure
