        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-jdbc-odbc-connection.dita#configure-jdbc-odbc-connection"
            >Configure a JDBC-ODBC <term>Connection</term>.</xref></li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view from the <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol>
